      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. one more thing, if we find that the items are just... gone without any obvious theft or data errors, what are some of the common ways businesses categorize that kind of \"mysterious\" shrinkage in their reports? like is there a specific term for items that just seem to vanish?",
